data.description: The single family waterfront pool home you have been waiting for! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage pool home is located on a quiet canal and has a fully fenced yard with plenty of room for the kids to play. Truly a home where you can move right in. Updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite counters and pantry. Newer tile/wood look flooring and freshly painted inside & out. Split bedroom floor plan, new hot water heater, Impact glass sliding doors, updated garage door, Roof 2015 & A/C 2014. NO HOA fee, no rental restrictions or pet restrictions. Excellent location just steps from Coconut Creek Elementary, close to park, major highways and shopping.
